org.orgName: Third Judicial District of Washington Territory, holding terms at Seattle

body.p: Office of the Sheriff of King County Washington Territory

I William Cochrane Sheriff of King County W.T do hereby certify that as the coming to me of the annexed writ of Habeas Corpus, the said, Joseph Bowers, was committed to my custody, and detained by virtue of a committment, a copy of which is hereto annexed there original of which I also herewith produce. Never the less I have the boody of the said Joseph Bowers before the Court at hour, day and place as I am in said writ commanded
Dated at Seattle W.T this 16th day of Dec, 1887
William Cochrane Sheriff of King County W.T. By. M Cadden Deputy
Sheriffs Fees Bringing in prisoner $1.00 Copy of commitment .40 Return .50 $1.90
